  "id": "ex_technical_5e168cb5",
  "intent": "Execute a Luminex assay sample replication protocol using a P300 multi-channel pipette to transfer specified sample volumes from source 24-well isopaks to multiple destination 24-well isopaks. For 24 samples, distribute each sample column-wise across 7 destination plates; for 48 samples, distribute across 6 destination plates using 2 source plates. Include optional exclusion of middle wells (columns 3-4) and implement volume tracking with re-aspiration when pipette capacity is exceeded.",
